ね、あたしのことが好きなら気づいて
Hey, if you love me, then realize it.

93
00:09:44,808 --> 00:09:47,308
気づいて 気づいて 気づいて
Realize it, realize it, realize it.

94
00:09:47,308 --> 00:09:51,108
夢を見せて落として分かってくれないの
Won't you show me a dream, drop me, and understand me?

95
00:09:51,108 --> 00:09:54,108
嫌いだ 嫌いだ 嫌いだ 嫌いだ
I hate you, I hate you, I hate you, I hate you.

96
00:09:54,108 --> 00:09:55,808
二度と触れないで
Never touch me again.

97
00:09:55,808 --> 00:09:59,008
全勝 1 2 の 3 で 流れ星
Total victory, on the count of 1, 2, 3, a shooting star,

